    <item>
      <title>瑞银的福勒表示，市场对法国大选的反应似乎有些过度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-24/ubs-fowler-overreaction-to-french-election-overdone-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银首席欧洲股票策略师兼衍生品主管 Gerry Fowler 表示，市场对法国大选的过度反应（提高欧洲风险溢价）似乎有些过头了。他在彭博简报中与 Manus Cranny 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-24/ubs-fowler-overreaction-to-french-election-overdone-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 10:04:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德称预计美联储今年将降息两次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-24/expect-fed-to-cut-rates-twice-this-year-blackrock-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德首席投资策略师李炜讨论了通货膨胀和央行降息问题。她表示，贝莱德预计美联储今年将降息两次，这与年初市场预期形成了“鲜明对比”。李炜在彭博电视台发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-24/expect-fed-to-cut-rates-twice-this-year-blackrock-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 09:55:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
