      <title>印度考虑降低小麦进口税以抑制价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/india-mulls-reducing-wheat-import-duty-to-tame-rising-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于供应日益紧张，印度正考虑罕见地削减小麦进口税，以控制价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/india-mulls-reducing-wheat-import-duty-to-tame-rising-prices</guid>
