      <title>债权人准备给予埃塞俄比亚更多时间与国际货币基金组织进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/creditors-ready-to-give-ethiopia-more-time-to-negotiate-imf-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位了解谈判情况的人士透露，埃塞俄比亚官方债权人准备将 6 月 30 日的最后期限延长，以便该国与国际货币基金组织就新计划达成协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/creditors-ready-to-give-ethiopia-more-time-to-negotiate-imf-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 09:43:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
